Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.store.disk

Provides the classes and interfaces of the MEKON Disk-Based Instance-Store Mechanism API (see uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon for general description).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMatcher
    Provides mechanisms for storing and executing queries over representations of sets of instantiations of a MEKON Frames Model (FM).
    IMatcherIndexes
    Provides mapping for each unique instance identity to a corresponding unique index value.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IDirectMatcher
    Provides an implementation of the reasoning mechanisms defined by IMatcher in which the matching is done directly on the frame/slot network representations of queries and instances.
    IDiskStoreBuilder
    Provides mechanisms for building a disk-based instance-store, as represented by an IStore object.
    ISimpleMatcherCore<I>
    Provides the core mechanisms for implementations of the reasoning mechanisms defined by IMatcher in which the matching is done directly on network representations of queries and instances.
